<s> <s> he was born at alcala de henares and baptised in the church of santa maria mayor on the 9th of october , 1547 . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> of his boyhood and youth we know nothing , unless it be from the glimpse he gives us in the preface to his  - comedies of himself as a boy looking on with delight while lope de rueda and his company set up their rude plank stage in the plaza and acted the rustic farces which he himself afterwards took as the model of his interludes . </s> </s> 
