<s> <s> cardenio also heard dorothea s cry as she fell fainting , and imagining that it came from his luscinda burst forth in terror from the room , and the first thing he saw was don fernando with luscinda in his arms . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> don fernando , too , knew cardenio at once; and all three , luscinda , cardenio , and dorothea , stood in silent amazement scarcely knowing what had happened to them . </s> </s> 
